# cry_pi — controlled-Ry(π). controlled-Ry = (I⊗Ry(φ/2))·CNOT·(I⊗Ry(-φ/2))·CNOT (표준 항등식). plan=봉인 cnot·ry_pi2·ry_negpi2, no MatrixGate.
```json id=app_meta
{"id": "cry_pi", "n_sys": 2, "n_anc": 0}
```
```python id=app_golden
import numpy as np
a = np.pi
Ry = np.array([[np.cos(a/2), -np.sin(a/2)], [np.sin(a/2), np.cos(a/2)]], dtype=complex)
golden = np.eye(4, dtype=complex); golden[2:, 2:] = Ry   # |1><1|⊗Ry, control=MSB
```
