{"steps": [{"spec": "../modules/cnot.pg", "targets": [0, 1]}, {"spec": "../modules/ry_negpi2.pg", "targets": [1]}, {"spec": "../modules/cnot.pg", "targets": [0, 1]}, {"spec": "../modules/ry_pi2.pg", "targets": [1]}]}
```
